Date: Fri, 8 May 2026 16:10:45 +0800
Subject: [PATCH] train: port adaptive weighting prerequisites

This ports the legacy lerobot_ros2 PR #13 adaptive-weighting foundations onto
the lerobot v0.5.1 base. It introduces the adaptive-weight config knobs,
returns frame indices from the dataset, exposes per-sample ACT losses, and
adds the sampler/training-loop glue that later weighted-training patches build
on.

